strings.Value: "Greetings, {mf|baron|baroness|King|Queen}. A good land you have here. So many seasoned warriors around. – More customers for old Varrask's weapons. I like it when there's so many good cutters around. I can breathe here, with fighters like these."

"Greetings! Yours is a strong army, {mf|baron|baroness|King|Queen}, and it seems you know how to keep an eye on those sneaky enemy scouts swarming around. But a little extra help wouldn't hurt, right?"
"Here, take this. It's my gift – it's a good one!"
